text:
Coffee blends are decent and they do serve a good cuppa. Dining environment is comfortable, well laid out and clean. I do question the service, or lack of. And I do hope the barista would stop his bl%@dy annoying habit of rocking the dosing lever on the grinder, or consider upgrading to an automated unit. We are paying to enjoy the environment (aside from the coffee) too.

Otherwise, %Cafe is a good place for your coffee fix.

Tasty coffee and soft serve ice cream
Close at 8 pm
Spanish latte was great. Reasonably strong but not bitter. Just the right amount of sweet. Croissant was very flaky and delicious
Mediocre coffee lacking any punch served. Coffee is above market price. No table service. Staffs' duties overlapping and not co-ordinated.
